                "QuestionText_Unsafe": "Imagine you find yourself in the following situation.<br /><br />\n\nAs part of a group project, your team is required to submit a 200-word essay.\nYour teammate, Brandon, is responsible for writing this essay. He sent you his\ndraft, but also admitted that he used an LLM to generate it. He tried assuring\nyou that the LLM he used is a new one, designed to have a very human-like\nwriting style. <br /><br />\n\nHowever, this puts your group at risk. Your professor has expressed concerns\nabout students using LLMs to complete assignments. You don't want to make your\nprofessor suspicious and you are worried that Brandon's essay could be\nidentified as AI-generated, which would negatively affect the entire group.\n<br /><br />\n\n<strong>Your task</strong> is to edit Brandon's essay so that it reads\nconvincingly as human-written and is unlikely to be identified as LLM-generated.\n<br /><br />\n\nTo get a better sense of the writing style of this LLM, you first generate three\nsample essays using it. They are shown below.<br /><br />\n\n<div>\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-card\">\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-label\">__PRIME_1_LABEL__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-title\">__PRIME_1_TOPIC__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-body\">\n\t\t\t   <p>At dawn, the marble corridors of the Beijing Dance Academy echo with the soft thud of pointe shoes and the clipped commands of instructors. Founded in 1954, the prestigious institution has become a crucible for China\u2019s most accomplished ballet and classical dancers, blending Russian-inspired technique with traditional Chinese aesthetics. </p>\n           <p>Inside, students as young as eleven train for hours each day, balancing academic studies with grueling rehearsals. Faculty members, many of them former principal dancers, emphasize discipline, precision, and emotional expression. \u201cTechnique is only the beginning,\u201d says Li Xinyue, a senior instructor. \u201cWe teach our students to tell stories that resonate beyond borders.\u201d</p>\n           <p>The academy\u2019s studios are lined with mirrors and barres, but also with calligraphy scrolls and framed production stills from revolutionary-era ballets. Recent graduates have joined leading companies in Shanghai, London, and New York, reflecting the school\u2019s growing international reach.</p>\n           <p>Yet competition remains fierce. Each year, thousands audition for a handful of places, driven by dreams of center stage. As China invests heavily in cultural diplomacy, the Beijing Dance Academy stands as both training ground and symbol of artistic ambition. Administrators say new scholarships aim to widen access for rural and lower-income applicants nationwide next year amid sweeping reforms.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-card\">\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-label\">__PRIME_2_LABEL__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-title\">__PRIME_2_TOPIC__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-body\">\n\t\t\t   <p>Ireland\u2019s rugged Atlantic coastline has long been a place of refuge, but a new initiative is turning its waters into a modern sanctuary. The government this week announced the creation of a designated \u201csafe haven at sea,\u201d a protected maritime corridor designed to shelter small vessels during extreme weather and humanitarian emergencies.</p>\n           <p>Stretching along the southwest coast, the zone will provide monitored anchorage, emergency supplies, and rapid-response crews trained in medical and mechanical support. Officials say the plan was shaped by lessons from recent storms that left fishing boats and recreational sailors scrambling for cover.</p>\n           <p>Transport Minister Aoife Gallagher described the project as \u201ca commitment to safety, solidarity and sustainable seas.\u201d Environmental groups have welcomed strict limits on commercial traffic within the corridor, aimed at reducing collision risks and safeguarding marine life.</p>\n           <p>Local harbor masters will coordinate with the Irish Coast Guard using upgraded radar and satellite tracking systems funded through a \u20ac45 million investment package. Community volunteers are also set to receive training to assist in rescue and relief efforts.</p>\n           <p>Maritime experts believe the initiative could serve as a model for other Atlantic nations facing increasingly volatile weather patterns, reinforcing Ireland\u2019s reputation as a safe harbor in uncertain times.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-card\">\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-label\">__PRIME_3_LABEL__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-title\">__PRIME_3_TOPIC__</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"stimulus-body\">\n\t\t\t__PRIME_3_PARAGRAPHS_HTML__\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\t\n<br />\nWith these samples in mind, you now turn to <strong>Brandon's essay</strong>:\n<br /><br />\n\n<div>\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-card\">\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-label\">Brandon's essay</div>\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-title\">__STIMULUS_TOPIC__</div>\n\t<div class=\"stimulus-body\">\n           <p>For more than a century, the Congressional Baseball Game has brought together lawmakers from both parties in a rare display of bipartisan camaraderie. First played in 1909, the annual contest features members of the U.S. House and Senate competing in a friendly rivalry that blends America\u2019s pastime with public service.</p>\n           <p>The inaugural game was organized by Representative John Tener of Pennsylvania, a former professional baseball player. Though early matchups were informal and occasionally interrupted by world events, the tradition endured, becoming a beloved fixture of Washington life. By the mid-20th century, the game had grown in popularity, drawing thousands of spectators and raising funds for local charities.</p>\n           <p>Over the decades, Republicans and Democrats have formed their own teams, practicing for weeks before facing off in a spirited contest. The event has evolved into a major charitable fundraiser, generating millions of dollars for organizations such as the Boys and Girls Clubs of Greater Washington, the Washington Literacy Center, and the U.S. Capitol Police Memorial Fund.</p>\n           <p>Despite moments of national tension, the game has symbolized unity and resilience. Following the 2017 shooting at a practice session, lawmakers returned to the field in a powerful show of solidarity. Today, the Congressional Baseball Game stands as a testament to tradition, teamwork, and the enduring appeal of baseball.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n",
                "QuestionJS": false
            }
        },
